title: Anyone received Oct 2020 security patch?
content:
It's currently the 1st Monday of the month of Oct and I still haven't received my Oct 2020 pixel security patch. I was wondering whether if it's just me or if anyone else is having this issue?

Also will this new update will it patch the chat bubbles bug which launched with Android 11?
And also the nearby share icon disappearing from the share sheet?

Your kind replies are highly appreciated. 
Thank you.
